@startuml EventFlow
title Event Flow: EVENTS → DELTAS → Projection

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

' Styling
skinparam rectangle {
    BackgroundColor<<source>> LightBlue
    BackgroundColor<<stream>> LightGreen
    BackgroundColor<<service>> LightYellow
    BackgroundColor<<storage>> LightGray
}

' Sources
rectangle "GitHub\nWebhook" as GH <<source>>
rectangle "Admin\nAPI" as ADMIN <<source>>

' EVENTS stream
queue "EVENTS Stream\n(JetStream)" as EVENTS

' Promoter
rectangle "Promoter Service\n\n• Validates schema\n• Checks event type\n• Applies gating rules\n• Filters duplicates" as PROMOTER <<service>>

' DELTAS stream
queue "DELTAS Stream\n(JetStream)" as DELTAS

' Projection
rectangle "Delta Projector\n\n• Consumes DELTAS\n• Updates current state\n• Maintains history\n• Binds provenance" as PROJECTOR <<service>>

' Storage
database "SQLite + FTS5\n\n• im_items_current\n• im_items_history\n• source_bindings\n• im_fts (search)" as DB <<storage>>

' Consumers
rectangle "Memory\nCompiler" as COMPILER <<service>>
rectangle "Replay\nEngine" as REPLAY <<service>>

' Flow
GH --> EVENTS : POST /api/v1/seed
ADMIN --> EVENTS : POST /api/v1/admin/rules

EVENTS --> PROMOTER : subscribe

PROMOTER --> DELTAS : publish\n(if valid)

DELTAS --> PROJECTOR : subscribe
DELTAS --> REPLAY : replay from seq 1

PROJECTOR --> DB : upsert

DB --> COMPILER : FTS5 query

note right of EVENTS
  **Immutable Log**
  All proposed changes
  (may include invalid)
end note

note right of DELTAS
  **Approved Changes Only**
  Source of truth for
  state reconstruction
end note

note bottom of DB
  **Derived State**
  Can be rebuilt by
  replaying DELTAS
  (proves H3)
end note

@enduml
